    dc:creator "Tong, Xiaoli; Wang, Zhaohong; Mirab-Balou, Majid" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Two new species and one new record of the genus Asprothrips (Thysanoptera: Thripidae) from China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256314>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256315>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256317> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256314>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Asprothrips bimaculatus: (1) female; (2) male. Asprothrips bucerus n. sp.: (3) female; (4) male. Asprothrips punctulosus n. sp.: (5) female; (6) male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/256314/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256315>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 13. Asprothrips bucerus n. sp.: (7) head and pronotum; (8) antenna of female; (9) antenna of male; (10) meso- and metanotum; (11) abdominal tergites IV – VI; (12) abdominal tergites IX – X; (13) fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/256315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.256317>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 23. Paramere shape of male genitalia; (21) A. bimaculatus; (22) A. bucerus n. sp.; (23) A. punctulosus n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/256317/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

